# Frontend Configuration
#
# NOTE: This project uses JSON configuration files instead of .env files.
# Configuration is loaded from /config/config.{environment}.json based on
# the Vite MODE (development, production, test).
#
# To configure the application:
# 1. Edit the appropriate JSON file in /config/ directory
# 2. Ensure all required values are present (no fallbacks - errors will be thrown)
#
# Available config files:
# - config/config.development.json (for local development)
# - config/config.production.json (for production builds)
# - config/config.test.json (for test environment)
#
# Required configuration values:
# - api.baseUrl: Backend API URL
# - auth0.domain: Auth0 tenant domain
# - auth0.clientId: Auth0 client ID
# - auth0.audience: Auth0 API audience
# - auth0.callbackUrl: Auth0 callback URL after authentication
#
# For local development, update config/config.development.json with your Auth0 credentials.
